  "text": "Siwalik Group Lewis (1937, p. 197) proposed a classification for the Siwalik Group following the principles of stratigraphic classification of [CITATION_1] . His classification, generally accepted by the writers, has been modified to comply with the Stratigraphic Code of Pakistan. Modifications inlude applying the lithostratigraphic rank \"group\" instead of Lewis' chronostratigraphic rank \"series.\"",
